  <description>
    <p>
      KeyVault is a secure 2FA/OTP manager that helps you store and manage all your two-factor
      authentication codes and time-based one-time passwords (TOTP) in one secure location.
    </p>
    <p>
      Features:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Secure storage for all your 2FA and OTP tokens</li>
      <li>Automatic TOTP code generation</li>
      <li>Easy organization of authentication codes</li>
      <li>Cross-platform support</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
